OL,5, An Indian government advertisement on  
OL,6, road safety is being criticised for    
OL,7, allegedly promoting dowry.             
OL,9,FThe ad, which features Bollywood star  
OL,10,FAkshay Kumar, was tweeted by federal   
OL,11,Ftransport minister Nitin Gadkari.      
OL,13,FIt shows Kumar scolding a father for   
OL,14,Fsending away his newly-wed daughter in 
OL,15,Fa car that has just two airbags.       
OL,17,FWhile some social media users praised  
OL,18,Fthe ad for highlighting safety, others 
OL,19,Ffelt it promoted dowry by hinting that 
OL,20,Fthe car was given by the father.       
